Package: LFUrmutils
Title: LFU risk management utilities
Version: 0.0-1
Date: 2019-06-11
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Bernhard", family = "Eder", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "bernhard.eder@uibk.ac.at"), 
  person(given = "David", family = "Ruppert", role = c("ctb"), email = "dr24@cornell.edu"), 
  person(given = "David S.", family = "Matteson", role = c("ctb"), email = "matteson@cornell.edu")
Depends: R (>= 3.0.0)
Imports: RQuantlib, stats, tseries, zoo
Suggests: fGARCH, lmtest, MTS, rugarch, rmgarch, xts
Description: Utility functions for the bachelor's seminar in risk management are provided.
  These include functions to compute (exponentially weighted) moving average models, 
  likelihood ratio tests for GARCH models, and some convenience functions 
  to make the output of various volatility models compareable.
